able width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igE6oFFbsMBo/v11/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Solar panels near electrical transformers at the Jeziorko PV solar farm, operated by PGE Energia Odnawialna SA, in Jeziorko, Poland, on Monday, Dec. 22, 2025. Poland’s electricity grid operator is preparing for a new reality where the stability of the system will no longer be provided by conventional energy sources as it seeks to avoid Spain-like blackouts. Photographer: Damian Lemanski&amp;amp;#x2F;Bloomberg" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="2025 年 12 月 22 日星期一，位于波兰 Jeziorko 的 Jeziorko 光伏太阳能发电厂的电力变压器附近的太阳能电池板，该发电厂由 PGE Energia Odnawialna SA 运营。波兰电网运营商正在为新的现实做准备，即系统的稳定性将不再由传统能源提供，因为它试图避免像西班牙那样的停电。摄影师：达米安·莱曼斯基&amp;amp;#x2F;彭博社" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igE6oFFbsMBo/v11/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;波兰电力变压器附近的太阳能电池板&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4; font-style: italic;"&gt;摄影师：达米安·莱曼斯基/彭博社&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;国际能源署在其 2025 年可再生能源&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/sGSWu78rRTlaqABaxJZJrlMo1egj9uOAfczUJIeZQ4osMSzZWX1P0njCAXhqbCbTprF3ap5yqOw1YuPBGBc02Uv4t3ULJwQd_YGpSkXJO1NppmmH_g0xxqNgCRI8UerSu7rEyxZ6dThQaevxuvP3o552DnfjRKFvGUFD6FgzrjCXJogaWIJRn3c2ZVxS76HgOLO4Y8EXFy1JO7pVURdIupDpqJ5Sqf7naD7Koy1UdF4T9k7c0Am-isbxrrKKCsb3XHXfVfUp_bGziiZNP7eFbLGI-eUdfwkq5hbChtYBCAG4h46PUrNjSpE8EvF7R8oQ8NOyXFD7PJ1WLTOVeF32q_qNJZPB6TNanvMfpZcxn3Ejxgl8fTwqry3qsUh7/OBvxN1AmSTUCm6gUjpFLcc9XJvmNswlv/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;报告&lt;/a&gt;中指出，配电、输电和互连能力问题限制了新可再生能源发电厂并网的速度，导致项目延误、成本上升和拍卖参与减少。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;巴克莱报告称，对于投资者来说，这些风险可以转化为创造跑赢市场回报的机会。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;汉纳说：“如果你能够识别这些瓶颈并提供缓解这些瓶颈的机制，那么就会创造阿尔法。”他指出，该报告并不反映该银行的内部观点，而是反映了作者的观点。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;阅读&lt;/em&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/OqpX8BwkcfoAGp-UaKNx8dBlr5ELgyOeeBs3ydyqkzDh5kZJ3zaATImXfxtrrcnD-acgUSae-R8Bmv18YTDVa69pe1G-4BBL6S6ww5tiyEeMfM7aX_bNQsc-w82EApf2JdZLsg2mJJN9zKpCkMwX9Hg2olggzHrz3iq8qLuJ8_sHdFrRNU2-2MfC-klXI9X9A0VWgNPGkkR4Gcpzu3erVF4dJJd30XjOyEsRQkINbuI1oPlzK2ouFRup6gBAHiLND13cICxshsJ9jw2zYvn1wVLtn_hubfM1LDIPa4iuSs8ThhH8GYrXS3byNdyluKaTZE0FfY1TB_6q1y5DV7etWvOFoUtc_aJ0mZfMaN12urejx3elQLXYbZeLTckpIw_Yi7qASSjLgl7NSbVQSPHKmbrTmOzDJtzF4AtxsYGQglU3shS0QGXCFmMKx2KryglCBzyKbMivHWoyFs6FAYJMwwgYl_cjOIUXvpvqU0QHg5lKC1MQeygGN_D58fBcZCNkUYDKRwK3lnYAam1xePWdjFsNj3AS-A1b67E/Od0J8ZP_VTwJzVZPTc-7XmRYRoxdliyb/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="巴克莱银行家看到可再生能源的不良资产风险"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;全文&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;，包括能源转型的下一步发展。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;table align="center" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="margin-top: 20px;" width="auto"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td align="center" style="padding: 0;" valign="top"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/Ww7u4iW1uXWINGAjllvlj9y20nObsCeypo9lUchQI9H_a7Yl1YSV6scoiqKBqooTW8gwrfv7NuY_Tvun5ZYqiuQ1pOFMQlBTNW6CJE6X1itFicssnzNznRkJPvU_S1LOc2gx1HBXCDuezC_pUTDSX0P89FaVjSl5KDRzBJ5PKTgWc_RVUtBWyaQ9V2sWzIUbgyUrYt3YjVwg58dyp2Fwjgg-LDm8g1rt2ddoDfJz5D3bZ-boVMNDmak6AQT_iXHrWuWrGx-H87gjmx3dwisn_g713MQKgMwQaloXCMY_rwyGVAoYMUh54zd84YpA7ZqtgX3l39W-r7IUXvSiSPraj9JLHbe7KLcV4CZiKJBaHGUnf1S2KxVUoC052C6Nb86aPOtu8KGWmAlsw7z9k-YwofAgteZtKXfByJmBa9xDI6keSnsKLjUzlP-qz_tvc_zNtIPGSL7J/Sb0x9QDukDXX0X41tQQv5QLx-A_sMxRN/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" border="0" class="m