8gIwNt8_KQM0CGbDd8JYOlMyq6quOEfF-eOk8DvyCdwfXA0EJ1h1POA664qPoyQcPiybPM6gpQrr5rOZ/Im0XLaErRx8v_O7GOa037si-KgJqSR__/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="伊朗战争愈演愈烈，特朗普承诺确保中东石油运输安全"&gt;打破这一泡沫&lt;/a&gt;。即使股市反弹，人们对韩国股市超常飙升的韧性的信心也不太可能完全恢复。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;公平地说，李在镕对Kospi指数的关注不仅仅是对科技巨头三星有利就是对韩国有利的简单想法，因为他试图让该国摆脱&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/482jo7fXZ7wWnLShJzBVv6eKaXj7OuODRC3giaB34HfaEve64fVTUNp6TfLR9UYAMzTEcDFnyoaK1P6nWa8nXwnq_K_cvQkGLMT2QOP2oYlPKjL5lCUzUCxocPhRRMNy6YH41yGLrUOjmCxux46cewlFddP3jQDF5LHl_D4co-aDfRDCJCO7L0WPYqP_DUpPW0LS1E8BXN3_YkNPG5QKIKvq4QRJzBAMH_sp73ViXEp-H3AkQVpUiefF_DfDPUeBbYW503E4erT69wKJpmQ_OUgUafEJR0ayaMV3KvJ-sXXRSRDPoBvpDe4WtOvax8WwVz25CFEU1LXpEJ-3IEoyXZ-kbGSZAR9TEsyFr2bQTn_hvz3D32XoOb2iTBm5Nkk2xB0Y86WLUyP9tjZt4ZGkUC4he-OCScfeLrudPNb9oN1Aa_3EnwIWdmjVUE_eqbKgpv4OqPgET4tDZhaZ2NndXiS5gZ9lLDWECflVkvnzxwRA0d8Lty3bJaDJjObLE3q2Sbe1UD3o0Zfp_4WPNyQ/w_jCtvgkAp18ZFZTORM1k987DrjBIdUs/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="总统称韩国房地产市场是一颗“定时炸弹”"&gt;长期对房地产的依赖&lt;/a&gt;，转向股票等资产。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/bvNHDZxnyv9btpbxvDDo9ikGvqUTFi8zDEqvNUf-_QsTOdkxeRg0p4C-rlOUaplw5W2kQo7ROPJesEDrEmFbiYYEbMZOacOcZPXqCdTaORX4H0_19G1EpyMKSvvsMgjtCLyRmBEE2vYDDpENVjCUe1rneeYcjbWV_UmvX6esV5ByCtCmcku33-HaRqslBLrj8uYmKudtbut_ScObOeMraci_RdzI8OlIkQcCA35C74Rt4VcIwyrZ7qhJ1kmH_B_CTkQSO74Xf0UazqSjPbSRJFgy3j3ClAwB7ocU9BH5ib2Q65MbWAvcauvTjS_RuQKu60A7f_J2gdvaJkjMoAms8xaAn4OUON3kW34r072szZeZ4AHsX3YEPxMf0hfBmK7hAtQCQqw/q5rzxEnKLUMPwrZUiex75ZvkMR5Afeho/18" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNTkSzhkBYtk/v47/-1x-1.jpg" alt="Korean stocks recorded their worst two-day drop since the 2008 financial crisis as the Iran conflict weighed on investor sentiment across the region. That&amp;amp;#39;s dragged down the Asian equity benchmark to its third day of losses. Bloomberg MLIV Strategist Mark Cranfield discusses the market moves on The China Show." width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="由于伊朗冲突打压了整个地区的投资者情绪，韩国股市录得自 2008 年金融危机以来最严重的两天跌幅。这导致亚洲股市基准指数连续第三个交易日下跌。彭博社 MLIV 策略师 Mark Cranfield 在中国秀上讨论市场走势。" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iNTkSzhkBYtk/v47/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;观看：彭博社 MLIV 策略师 Mark Cranfield 讨论最新情况。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;问题在于，它的进展有点过于顺利，而全球人工智能的反弹又提振了韩国芯片制造商，从而放大了这一情况。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;在大张旗鼓地突破 5,000 家里程碑之后——随后迅速突破 6,000 家大关——一些初出茅庐的投资者可能在错误的时间到达了聚会。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;业余所谓散户投资者的参与激增。许多企业都面临着巨大损失。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;随着恐慌的出现，韩国央行行长李昌镛推迟了前往曼谷举行的金融首脑峰会的行程，以便就此次事件的后果召开紧急会议。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;坠机事件发生时，李今天在菲律宾，他将于明天召开特别内阁会议，讨论战争的影响。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;李的人气受到的打击还有待观察。但可以公平地说， &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/UeUKKsSp9ajqfUSyQRi38TxTnJElw4g3B1i_ErkYhRpoyGhZcbRq4nmd_95EvzDKabSXPHzpLmNEHUSrmMca8Tt7LDCyLDyFTmoa5izMi-UmmScekkELQfjOFDPYucl7d-IzCxpe6BNiVDM_QHkYDJVDolfcMCzqSCd3nwY8FjC2b5LRs3n9TKwTMCPurvRvqlICS2g-wWi5E7MrgPvT0Zk9EYGoBY0cW5R5Govf0XS-lzaHVy2fGWvhhgB_5QkEPwRHQEcsroEbkc9_5lfg6IZMkDwwlLjq9oSSY3ewtE_DHAaPilgK9lbJiLNQEivSgYXi_JOlsCHQ_os6frePcB4NKHXtXFTG6kprMBeR-wlUs6cUyTOl5CiotpYhtWBiGCbDa-Hh-WjDU1cyxr3-h03LKqWQ4pyJmm1UN1LevhRpEXFQXlqUZqmFfuo1VFHmGZSy00XsWAMZ33pi1hAQmo_4PRDMZ8fN4AYBnaf_MXL3AWdU8cXe9TsEzuvZUrkv-