t on Tuesday. During the meeting, Merz told Trump he wants the European Union’s trade agreement with the US to be implemented quickly but that the bloc can’t accept a deal with worse conditions. Merz also said that the US couldn’t impose prohibitive trade measures just on Spain, after Trump threatened to cut off all trade with Madrid after the country denied access to its military bases for the American bombing campaign against Iran. Bloomberg&amp;amp;#39;s Oliver Crook reports." width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="美国总统唐纳德·特朗普和德国总理弗里德里希·梅尔茨周二会面。会议期间，默茨告诉特朗普，他希望欧盟与美国的贸易协定能够迅速实施，但欧盟不能接受条件更差的协议。默茨还表示，在西班牙拒绝进入其军事基地参与美国对伊朗的轰炸行动后，特朗普威胁要切断与马德里的所有贸易，美国不能只对西班牙实施禁止性贸易措施。彭博社的奥利弗·克鲁克报道。" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/is7BR.boNMkA/v47/-1x-1.jpg" style="width: 100%; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;figcaption&gt;&lt;div style="font-size: 14px; line-height: 1.4;"&gt;观看：彭博电视台的奥利弗·克鲁克报道特朗普与梅尔茨的会面。&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/figcaption&gt;&lt;/figure&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;菲律宾国会一个小组&lt;/strong&gt;提出对副总统萨拉·杜特尔特提出两项弹劾指控，这对小费迪南德·马科斯总统的政治对手&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/MpJvgFRx2CFBjOGw3qafHIoiy3k-kYDbxIFVYu0bDrrBIYaJaFdWtgJiun4loqu7LlxJ5xbRxYk3cYS5mxdwbijg2pXaLPwOp-pL8xX78nQn-YhI8-uq_VDMXAnRuQwhzEqtkvz6kf-ucYAIwb6OFpXsM0ia6KKE6jzbwoMQQb31-U2jkax86ArASJAisD_Od6R8hjspc4UFbG4P7BGjmEjk9fV_zw854v9iZAGvrHYHEZ9_y9YrPvfuTnqS2Cm65--5HNQBkYveFowvG-fYMb876Iy-N-woKM_IQCs7CEyyoqXNHHlJE7I3AKbZOC7uxFG81xsiti9RfZMsxXV-skydSOa6r0z5l2himUiYWHZXftp5_U2Ddr2eTOVY73XPnoEW5BYrHL4TL0nsxDbnSSEskmm2y672waga2et3FjYeIYeS_6n4pdMNON6Bv6SPUCjzd9gUvPGlqDPN3rn3t9tkuNfFOb5zgwh_pV1UTlIi1R3pHrIdo654tSB_JjbQPW7oVCjZmttkgLMjiTx6zQ/YPIw_UvcxIZRyFv7_w6_2wI4f211u688/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="菲律宾议员推进弹劾副总统杜特尔特"&gt;造成了打击，&lt;/a&gt;后者否认威胁暗杀马科斯和滥用公共资金的指控。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;尼日利亚提前了明年的选举时间表&lt;/strong&gt;，并宣布了新规则，这似乎让反对派措手不及，人们&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/xtPpk4-3h92UklMofK8FM42kRDUEalUSgIwd_SBTOIKPWHBpsg1NlKWdXqOpQmbmCikqZ-fBm8Izzk3uuXWvl5-hqokdUFnoU9xHwCCCUHqddna3O8iuT4HCrOKsNp5Em-5oQ4kg_TqIDdpNCZhGF7oU430TBhKyTnxsqCfaPgB06MFiyANMgZW-WPsSmcNRVEg8IrmIDi5gZzsSMDiVHma3gWZX6i8yBRG6kZwjpFYw0t7Hf1QxqgrlGBZQB32Pod-KyF6eev0JZ2SYDEwkdaP4fVlVLQM57Sxn_qAMHNg8uHcCLeU5BYe5yJLB2nGy4kbWxsBj2cNevtHsnaMcjQKVA_8UnrU29Svl1BvnOtpSKr9Um-rROtdRlwBGEkcZpAJePX_Khyr0piHoz_Ldkv7BhdY-IpWJhwceRY87GpFZVkZHHYPZriI2p_DQOMjUB6xR0trqKlxvtS8tAhLY21uHtI1QFIEZK05BtXRzN33tnjBzQ51GMnn73izjdR4kkkXhoEMGo-FWFLDRtxKpDA/_nQy5GgISducfmQrqgRujg6MNaBRC294/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="尼日利亚进入选举季，反对派奋起直追"&gt;普遍预计&lt;/a&gt;总统博拉·蒂努布将继续掌权。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/lQ6Mv8IAz3CB2OEYO_auJqXRJYkNyLM8BmTi0vAB3DLy-3FmwO8SDwykYVlkcMu1JmgKhZ9IxKemqcHE2dTpZRafXVRi9OJt0IBYSUl0MsP0b8Gs33iy295rI25BCcZJwNpCtSe5tco-HHsXQx74HjZ-631bg9xZ4ls1I08DkGc2aPdrZ_h_-dCgXBwR-EDrPoKno54ZNqkRAQ5eq_u_sIfUv_XoTcN_MFC_fDp0de-sk_U0eODDhAnsDcOIa1mMKFAUtcoYRnghpjOxD5dKKRqLYYgVw_osV3Xb6uWU2b939QwVmMdhYfkjcq6I35OJaGye6rw/oAJ4umG0cL7Q2r9QdGK5bSqnYAKnefYw/18" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;订阅华盛顿版时事通讯，&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;了解来自美国首都的新闻，并在美国东部时间工作日下午 1 点和 5 点观看彭博电视台的《权力平衡》节目。&lt;/em&gt; &lt;/p&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;每日图表&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i